    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1-1623400279031-x200.jpg",
