      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 4,
