    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>sliced shallot</strong> to the pan with the chicken</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the tomatoes have started to soften</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1713792850087-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1713792850087-x400.jpg",
